Five Year Accident History:
This is a new facility.  

Emergency Response Program:
The Whitetail Gas Processing Plant Emergency Response Plan has been coordinated with the Elk County Control Office.  The plan has been posted at the plant and all employees have been trained in the actions to be taken in the event of an emergency.

Planned Changes to Improve Safety:
No changes to the safety program or plant facilities are currently planned. However, regular safety meetings are held during which incidents are reviewed, safety procedures discussed and changes proposed.  Our safety program is constantly improving
